rows.label: qev060505_MSG0001
rows.name:
Tank choked on garbage. So I hit it. Then it got angry.
So I hit harder. Then it started smoking.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060505_MSG0002
rows.name:
Human machines are complicated.
I miss simple Prone machines.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060505_MSG0003
rows.name:
Masked ones would be useful when fighting coward
who uses poison gas.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060505_MSG0004
rows.name: New workers came. Looked around. Ran away.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060505_MSG0005
rows.name:
They are cowards. My body is strong from training.
I am not afraid. But I still don't know how machines
work. Ha ha ha![ST:wait ]
